l look back at past operating systems and wish Windows 11 could draw inspiration from them.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eWell, however you feel about Windows 11, Microsoft seems to be pretty chuffed with it. In fact, they\u0026#39;re so pleased that they\u0026#39;ve stated that Windows 1124H2 is the most reliable Windows yet. And as it turns out, the company isn\u0026#39;t just making that claim on a vibe.\u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                    \n                        \n    \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"b4fe-47f8-a4afcae97578\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n        \n        \n                        \t\n\t                \n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.xda-developers.com/microsoft-reveals-windows-11-25h2-release-soon/\"\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/06/windows-11-with-explorer-7.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/06/windows-11-with-explorer-7.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/upload